<item chapnbr="27" chg="U" itemnbr="2" key="UPS747MEL20070815103251" revdate="20080827" revnbr="5" sectnbr="81">
<title>Leading Edge Flaps Drives &ndash; (Electric)</title>
<dispcond category="C" maintenance="YES" nbrins="8" nbrreq="7"
operation="NO" btb="YES">
<remarks>
<para>One may be inoperative provided:</para>
<numlist>
<numlitem><para>All pneumatic drives are operative, and</para>
</numlitem>
<numlitem><para>Associated electric drive is deactivated.</para>
</numlitem>
</numlist>
</remarks>
<operation key="UPS747MEL20070815103252">
<note><para>The following EICAS message(s) may be displayed:</para>
<para>LE SINGLE DRIVE</para>
</note>
</operation>
<placard>
<para>Placard near flap lever: "NUMBER ___ L (R) ELEC DR INOP". Enter
item in Aircraft Deferred Item Log. </para>
</placard>
<maintenance key="UPS747MEL20070815103253">
<para>Deactivate the associated electric drive.</para>
<numlist>
<numlitem><para>Extend the leading edge flaps pneumatically (AMM 27-81-00). </para>
</numlitem>
<numlitem><para>Check the Primary EICAS Display to ensure that all
leading edge flaps are extended to the correct position.</para>
</numlitem>
<numlitem><para>Remove pneumatic power (AMM 36-00-00/201).</para>
</numlitem>
<numlitem><para>Open the following circuit breakers and attach DO-NOT-CLOSE
tags:</para>
<table frame="none">
<tgroup cols="3">
<colspec colname="col1" colwidth="163.43pt"/>
<colspec colname="col2" colwidth="148.65pt"/>
<colspec colname="col3" colwidth="197.92pt"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry align="center" colsep="0" rowsep="0" valign="top">
<para><emphasis role="underline">P-6 Panel</emphasis></para>
</entry>
<entry align="center" colsep="0" rowsep="0" valign="top">
<para><emphasis role="underline">P-414 Panel</emphasis></para>
</entry>
<entry align="center" colsep="0" rowsep="0" valign="top">
<para><emphasis role="underline">P-415 Panel</emphasis></para>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry colsep="0" rowsep="0">
<para>PRI LE FLAP CONT GRP A AC</para>
<para>PRI LE FLAP CONT GRP A DC</para>
<para>PRI LE FLAP CONT GRP B AC</para>
<para>PRI LE FLAP CONT GRP A DC</para>
<para>LE FLAP ELEC CONT GRP B</para>
<para>DRIVE 1</para>
<para>LE FLAP ELEC CONT GRP A</para>
<para>DRIVE 2</para>
<para>LE FLAP ELEC CONT GRP A</para>
<para>DRIVE 3</para>
<para>LE FLAP ELEC CONT GRP A</para>
<para>DRIVE 4</para>
</entry>
<entry colsep="0" rowsep="0">
<para>LE FLAP ELEC DRIVE 1</para>
<para>LE FLAP ELEC DRIVE 4</para>
</entry>
<entry colsep="0" rowsep="0">
<para>LE FLAP ELEC DRIVE 2</para>
<para>LE FLAP ELEC DRIVE 3</para>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</numlitem>
<numlitem><para>Locate the associated electric drive motor in the
leading edge wing cavity, remove and securely stow alternate drive
motor&rsquo;s electrical connector.</para></numlitem>
<numlitem><para>Close circuit breakers opened above.</para></numlitem>
</numlist>
